### Audit + observability

- App stdout/stderr is captured by the `logs-sink` pipeline (separate
  bundle in this repo's `logs-sink/` dir). It writes structured rows to
  `audit_catalog`.`audit`.`app_events`.
- Drift detection: `.github/workflows/drift-detection.yml` runs hourly
  and compares the deployed app's `EXPECTED_GIT_SHA` against the latest
  `main` SHA. Mismatch → it opens an issue.
- The app refuses to start if `EXPECTED_GIT_SHA` is unset. This catches
  manual workspace-UI uploads.
